cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is primarily focused on robotics and manipulation, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the cs.RO (Robotics) sub-category. The paper also discusses visual feedback and learning, which suggests that it may also belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-categories. The use of reinforcement learning further supports the possibility of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) being a relevant sub-category. Finally, the discussion of transferring the model to a real-world robot suggests that cs.SY (Systems and Control) may also be a relevant sub-category.
